title: The Processor
desc: The Processor is a hub for all your cyber-punk needs.

title: The Plaza
desc: You stand in a large plaza with computerized billboards all over. A steady stream of cars can be seen flying overhead.

title: First Bank of Binary
desc: You have entered the first bank of binary. This bank has been around for ages. The walls look rustic, circa 2018.

title: West Central St
desc: You stand at the dead end of Central St. There is nothing but but a few pieces of trash blowing around.

title: West Riff St.
desc: You stand on Riff St. This dark and dilapidated street has seen better days.

title: West Central St.
desc: You are nearing the end of Central St. There is nothing but dilapidated buildings here.

title: Riff St./Qualconn St.
desc: You stand at the intersection of Riff St. and Qualconn St.

title: South Qualconn St.
desc: You stand on Qualconn St. The street named after a now defunct mobile processing manufacturer.

title: South Qualconn St.
desc: You are on Qualconn St. There is an alley to the east that runs to Harden St.

title: South Qualconn St.
desc: The alley is still there to the east.

title: South Qualconn St.
desc: You are on Qualconn St. There isn't much around.

title: West Central St.
desc: You are on the corner of Qualconn St. and Central St.
